22
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:25,829
Except those three, 
she bought the other 997.

23
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:31,234
So what? Just because she's
the owner? But I'm the brain!

24
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:33,550
Nonsense! 
I'm leaving for Paris!

25
