we'll talk about it later.

919
01:22:16,280 --> 01:22:20,239
Are you a soccer 
or a sportscar champion?

920
01:22:20,480 --> 01:22:22,232
Soccer!

921
01:22:34,880 --> 01:22:40,238
I'm feeling cold, 
if we'd get a cup of tea...

922
01:22:40,480 --> 01:22:43,435
Thanks but I don't have time. 
Where's your cousin?

923
01:22:43,480 --> 01:22:45,235
Wait on a minute. 
We came all the way here...

924
01:22:45,480 --> 01:22:48,234
Give me the money 
and I'll take it to her.

925
01:22:48,280 --> 01:22:50,634
I need 
to give it personally.

926
01:22:50,880 --> 01:22:53,474
- So, will you wait for me here?
- With pleasure!

927
01:23:21,800 --> 01:23:26,032
- How come are you here?
- I wanted to go for a trip.

928
01:23:26,280 --> 01:23:30,239
- With your beautiful lady.
- No, it's over.

929
01:23:30,480 --> 01:23:35,031
- By the way, you mentioned 
of a girl... - Well, she's here.

930
01:23:35,280 --> 01:23:39,432
- Here?
- she's smart, elegant...

931
01:23:39,680 --> 01:23:42,831
- Enough, I accept!
- Without seeing her?

932
01:23:43,080 --> 01:23:45,835
As long as you like her. 
Is she a cripple? No! 

933
01:23:45,880 --> 01:23:47,835
Hunchback? No! 
So, I'll marry her then.

934
01:23:48,080 --> 01:23:51,152
I'll get engaged 
this very night.

935
01:23:51,400 --> 01:23:57,032
Tell her that she has my agreement,
or rather that I am in love.

936
01:24:01,480 --> 01:24:03,675
- May I?
- You again!

937
01:24:03,920 --> 01:24:06,639
Yes, me again,
but for few seconds only!

938
01:24:06,880 --> 01:24:11,228
Just the time to give you 
these printed sheets!

939
01:24:11,250 --> 01:24:13,228
They aren't written,
but printed!

940
01:24:13,480 --> 01:24:17,029
- Have you come here on purpose?
- No, I'm passing by.

941
01:24:17,280 --> 01:24:21,432
- Good luck, Countess.
- Thanks, same to you.

942
01:24:21,680 --> 01:24:23,958
- Are you leaving now?
- No, I'm staying just 

943
01:24:23,990 --> 01:24:25,958
for a formality. I'm 
gonna get engaged tonight.

944
01:24:26,200 --> 01:24:30,637
Really? Congratulations, 
when will you marry?

945
01:24:30,880 --> 01:24:33,838
- I don't know yet but soon, within
the current month! - What a hurry!

946
01:24:34,080 --> 01:24:36,676
Are you afraid 
to change your mind?

947
01:24:36,680 --> 01:24:38,676
No, I'm determined 
and very much in love.

948
01:24:38,920 --> 01:24:42,435
How touching! 
Is your fiancée beautiful?

949
01:24:42,680 --> 01:24:47,834
I don't know... I mean, I know it!
She's beautiful and, above all, nice.

950
01:24:48,080 --> 01:24:54,474
Nice, affectionate and loyal.
Do you know what 'loyal' means?

951
01:24:54,720 --> 01:24:59,555
- It's not one of those women who are...
- I wish you a lot of happiness.

952
01:24:59,800 --> 01:25:06,239
But make sure not 
letting such a nice girl...

953
01:25:06,480 --> 01:25:10,951
waiting too long because of me!
- You're wrong!

954
01:25:11,200 --> 01:25:18,231
- My fiancée... - I've got to go 
to the tailor and measure a dress.

955
01:25:18,480 --> 01:25:21,271
Actually, if you come back 
in 10 minutes, I also 

956
01:25:21,280 --> 01:25:24,271
want to give you 
an advice and some news.

957
01:25:24,520 --> 01:25:27,159
Very well, 
see you later Countess!

958
01:25:27,920 --> 01:25:30,992
(host) Engagement!

959
01:25:37,960 --> 01:25:40,269
First kiss.

960
01:25:52,640 --> 01:25:55,029
Waiting.

961
01:26:26,080 --> 01:26:29,231
What a surprise, isn't it? 
It suits me, don't you think?

962
01:26:29,480 --> 01:26:33,473
It feels a bit funny 
in here but it's nothing.

963
01:26:33,720 --> 01:26:36,829
You look so surprised because 
you don't know my name. 

964
01:26:36,920 --> 01:26:39,829
Everybody talked 
about it these days!

965
01:26:40,080 --> 01:26:43,231
But you could've seen 
it on the papers.

966
01:26:43,480 --> 01:26:49,430
I obtained my marriage dissolution
and tomorrow I'll get married here.

967
01:26:49,680 --> 01:26:52,334
It's a strange idea, 
but we're a group of friends.

968
01:26:52,480 --> 01:26:54,834
and here it'll 
be more cheerful.

969
01:26:55,080 --> 01:26:57,232
Weddings are always depressing.

970
01:26:57,280 --> 01:26:59,232
Of course! 
You know that by experience!

971
01:26:59,480 --> 01:27:02,916
- That dress has an imperfection.
- What?

972
01:27:03,160 --> 01:27:07,676
- Yes, orange flowers.
- Orange flowers?

973
01:27:07,920 --> 01:27:10,438
I heard they 
are a symbol of purity...

974
01:27:10,520 --> 01:27:13,438
When a man insults 
a woman, he's a lout...

975
01:27:30,680 --> 01:27:33,896
Go away, you insulted me enough!
It's all over now!

976
01:27:33,980 --> 01:27:36,596
I wouldn't start 
it again for anything!

977
01:27:36,840 --> 01:27:39,274
Go then once 
and for all. I'm busy!

978
01:27:39,520 --> 01:27:43,718
Yes! For a woman like you 
marriage is just a dress!

979
01:27:43,960 --> 01:27:50,593
Better a poor common girl, 
a tailor, a hatter...

980
01:27:50,840 --> 01:27:54,515
those who live 
because they work! Understand?

981
01:27:54,760 --> 01:27:58,719
They've got heart, 
they know what love is...

982
01:27:58,960 --> 01:28:03,033
and embody more nobility than 
all the countesses on earth.

983
01:28:03,280 --> 01:28:05,939
That's how I wanted my woman, 
uncomplicated, 

984
01:28:05,950 --> 01:28:07,239
without frills and jewels.

985
01:28:07,480 --> 01:28:12,235
- But with a big heart!
- Can't you see what I am?

986
01:28:12,480 --> 01:28:15,278
- What are you?
- A mannequin!

987
01:28:15,520 --> 01:28:19,035
In italian it's "fashion model". 
That's what you say!

988
01:28:19,280 --> 01:28:23,637
You? And do you work 
in my aunty's firm?

989
01:28:23,680 --> 01:28:25,037
Yes, at Primavera Stores!

990
01:28:25,280 --> 01:28:31,992
So I know where to find you then!
Via Roma, 148. Telephone: 62347!

991
01:28:32,240 --> 01:28:35,038
What an idea! Great! Great!

992
01:28:41,000 --> 01:28:46,393
- I withdraw my resignation
- You withdraw your ideas! - Sure.
